    {
        "content": "<p>Do you really need metric instead of pseudo-metric in the second part of Theorem 4.20? I thought a recent discussion on Zulip showed it was not necessary?</p>",
        "id": 560560646,
        "sender_full_name": "Sébastien Gouëzel",
        "timestamp": 1764238831
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>To get a modification in the sense of equality, you need it. Not to get a modification in the sense of distance zero. We did not add that discussion to the paper, but perhaps we should.</p>",
        "id": 560560846,
        "sender_full_name": "Rémy Degenne",
        "timestamp": 1764238892
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>6 messages were moved here from <a class=\"stream-topic\" data-stream-id=\"509433\" href=\"/#narrow/channel/509433-Brownian-motion/topic/Status.20of.20the.20project/with/544333072\">#Brownian motion &gt; Status of the project</a> by <span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"350992\">Rémy Degenne</span>.</p>",
        "id": 560561099,
